       The forms package establishes initial current default val-
       ues for field attributes.   During  field  initialization,
       each field attribute is assigned the current default value
       for that attribute.  An application can change or retrieve
       a current default attribute value by calling the appropri-
       ate set or retrieve routine with a NULL field pointer.  If
       an  application  changes a current default field attribute
       value, subsequent fields created using new_field will have
       the  new default attribute value.  (The attributes of pre-
       viously created  fields  are  not  changed  if  a  current
       default attribute value is changed.)

